Browse cameras without driving, tap for details, robust live update

- Idle map now one-shot centers on your location so nearby cameras are visible
  before you start a drive (previously only showed after Start Driving)
- Tap any camera dot to open a detail card (name, brand, facing, purpose,
  operator, zone, distance, photo) with pointer cursor + close button
- Make "Update cameras (live)" reliable: 3 Overpass mirrors with failover,
  100s AbortController timeout, empty-result guard, and human-readable errors
